Spike looked around the room "so were is everyone"he asked "usually 
talon is here to greet us, but he's not here" spike said walking out 
of the docking bay and down the hall towards the command center "I'll 
look outside and u check in the base" spike said before running 
towards the ramp, when he got outside he saw where talon had taken 
off and spike quickly got the idea that something was 
happening "crusher i want u to stay here I'm going to find talon"he 
said into his com before he rolled up into his ball and shot away 
leaving a trail of dust behind him
